const CONSTANTS = {}

CONSTANTS.ERROR_MESSAGE = {}

CONSTANTS.ERROR_MESSAGE.GRID_GET = 'Request to get grid text failed:'

CONSTANTS.ERROR_MESSAGE.MASTERDETAIL_GET = 'Request to get master detail text failed:'

CONSTANTS.ERROR_MESSAGE.DIRECTUSAUTH_POST = 'Request to auth failed:'

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT = {}

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.GRID = '/api/grid'

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.MASTERDETAIL = 'https://stint-api.onrender.com/api/masterdetail'

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.DIRECTUSAUTH = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/auth/login'

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.DIRECTUSEMAIL = 'stint.assess@gmail.com'

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.DIRECTUSPASSWORD = 'dstintapp1'

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.GETASSESSMENTSESSION = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/items/Assessment_Session?access_token='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.GETCANDIDATE = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/items/Candidate?access_token='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.GETJOBSKILLS = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/items/Job_Skill?access_token='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.POSTCANDIDATEPROFILE = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/items/Candidate_Profile?access_token='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.POSTCANDIDATESKILL = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/items/Candidate_Skill?access_token='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.GETQUESTION = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/items/Question?access_token='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.POSTSESSIONRECORDING = 'https://stint-api.onrender.com/api/sessionrecord'

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.POSTEVALUATION = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/items/Assessment_Evaluation?access_token='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.GETSPEECHURL = 'https://freetts.com/Home/PlayAudio?Language=en-IN&Voice=en-IN-Standard-C&TextMessage='

CONSTANTS.ENDPOINT.GETSPEECHFILE = 'https://bcbsp806.directus.app/assets/<asset-id>.mp3?access_token='

export default CONSTANTS
